==Finnish==
{{Finnish index|ki}}

===Etymology===
Earlier, ''kirja'' meant something like "carved mark/decoration" [1] and some derived terms get their meaning from the former sense. The Estonian cognate ''[[kiri#Estonian|kiri]]'' means "letter (to be sent)".

===Noun===
'''kirja'''

# [[book]].
# [[chapter]] in the [[Bible]] or another book.

